I BELIEVE MOST OF
YOU KNOW BENEDICK...

00:14:02.300 --> 00:14:05.600
AND OUR NEW
DIRECTOR, PETER.

00:14:05.600 --> 00:14:08.400
WE'RE VERY EXCITED TO HAVE
THEM BACK, AND TO SHOW

00:14:08.400 --> 00:14:12.560
JUST HOW PLEASED I'D LIKE
TO HAND OVER TO HERO...

00:14:12.560 --> 00:14:14.530
UH, HERO?

00:14:14.530 --> 00:14:16.300
OH, SORRY.

00:14:16.300 --> 00:14:18.760
WE'VE DECIDED WE'RE
GOING TO HAVE A PARTY

00:14:18.760 --> 00:14:21.900
SUNDAY NIGHT, DAD'S HOUSE
TO WELCOME THE NEW TEAM.

00:14:21.900 --> 00:14:24.860
