THE LETTERS, THE PHONE
CALLS, THE FLOWERS.

00:15:00.760 --> 00:15:02.600
I CAN BUY SOMEONE
FLOWERS, CAN'T I?

00:15:02.600 --> 00:15:04.260
NOT ANYMORE, NO.

00:15:04.260 --> 00:15:06.830
I'M VERY GRATEFUL, BUT...

00:15:06.830 --> 00:15:12.630
WELL, I'M WITH CLAUDE NOW
AND I LIKE HIM VERY MUCH.

00:15:12.630 --> 00:15:16.330
BUT I'VE NEVER FELT LIKE THIS
ABOUT SOMEONE BEFORE.

00:15:16.330 --> 00:15:18.400
NOT EVEN MY WIFE.

00:15:18.400 --> 00:15:20.830
HERO...?

00:15:20.830 --> 00:15:24.330
YOU'RE ASHAMED OF ME.
THAT'S IT, ISN'T IT?

00:15:24.330 --> 00:15:28.330
THAT'S WHY WE'RE WAY OUT HERE
SO NO ONE ELSE CAN SEE US.

00:15:28.330 --> 00:15:30.400
I SEE YOU OUTSIDE
THE HOUSE, DON.

00:15:30.400 --> 00:15:32.800
SITTING IN YOUR CAR IN
THE MIDDLE OF THE NIGHT.

00:15:32.800 --> 00:15:35.560
IT'S NOT FAIR. I DON'T
LIKE IT, IT SCARES ME.

00:15:35.560 --> 00:15:36.860
I'M SORRY.

00:15:36.860 --> 00:15:39.300
YOU CAN'T FORCE SOMEONE
TO LOVE YOU, DON.

00:15:39.300 --> 00:15:41.800
YOU CAN'T FORCE
THEM NOT TO EITHER.

00:15:41.800 --> 00:15:44.460
BUT YOU WILL FIND
SOMEBODY ELSE.

00:15:44.460 --> 00:15:46.830
I KNOW YOU WILL,
YOU'RE A LOVELY MAN.

00:15:46.830 --> 00:15:48.360
AM I?

00:15:48.360 --> 00:15:50.560
OF COURSE YOU ARE.

00:15:50.560 --> 00:15:54.760
THAT NIGHT WE
SPENT TOGETHER...

00:15:54.760 --> 00:15:58.230
IT WASN'T BECAUSE YOU
FELT SORRY FOR ME?

00:15:58.230 --> 00:16:00.600
OF COURSE NOT.

00:16:00.600 --> 00:16:04.330
YOU WERE JUST
LONELY, THAT'S ALL.

00:16:04.330 --> 00:16:07.100
YOU'LL FIND SOMEONE
ELSE, LIKE I FOUND CLAUDE,

00:16:07.100 --> 00:16:10.100
AND YOU'LL FALL
IN LOVE AGAIN,

00:16:10.100 --> 00:16:14.430
AND THEN WE CAN GO BACK
TO BEING GOOD FRIENDS.

00:16:18.660 --> 00:16:22.530
I NEED THIS TO BE
OUR SECRET, OKAY?

00:16:22.530 --> 00:16:27.430
YEAH.

00:16:27.430 --> 00:16:30.900
WELL, WHAT A LOT OF WEATHER
WE'VE BEEN HAVING RECENTLY.

00:16:30.900 --> 00:16:32.800
LOOK AT HER.

00:16:32.800 --> 00:16:36.000
THE WAY SHE BRINGS THE SUN IN
WITH THE WAVE OF HER HAND.

00:16:36.000 --> 00:16:38.900
