MAKING IT HAPPEN FOR REAL,

00:16:38.900 --> 00:16:40.930
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT I MEAN?

00:16:40.930 --> 00:16:43.300
YOU'RE NOT GOING TO DO
ANYTHING STUPID, ARE YOU?

00:16:43.300 --> 00:16:44.860
LIKE WHAT?

00:16:44.860 --> 00:16:46.560
THE "M" WORD.

00:16:46.560 --> 00:16:48.530
NO, 'COURSE NOT.

00:16:48.530 --> 00:16:52.760
BUT IT WOULDN'T BE SUCH
A BAD IDEA, WOULD IT?

00:16:52.760 --> 00:16:55.060
IF YOU SAY SO.

00:16:55.060 --> 00:16:57.660
YOU DON'T THINK
SHE'S GORGEOUS?

00:16:57.660 --> 00:16:59.800
SHE'S VERY
NICE, CLAUDE.

00:16:59.800 --> 00:17:05.330
I JUST PREFER SOMETHING
A LITTLE LESS... OBVIOUS.

00:17:05.330 --> 00:17:08.360
LIKE WHAT?
I MEAN, WHO?

00:17:08.360 --> 00:17:12.260
I DON'T KNOW.
HER, I SUPPOSE.

00:17:12.260 --> 00:17:14.200
BEATRICE?

00:17:14.200 --> 00:17:16.360
IT'S A PURELY
OBJECTIVE STATEMENT.

00:17:16.360 --> 00:17:18.700
LIKE COMPARING A
LOTUS TO A PORSCHE.

00:17:18.700 --> 00:17:20.900
BIT SEXIST COMPARING
A WOMAN TO A CAR?

00:17:20.900 --> 00:17:22.730
DEPENDS ON THE CAR.

00:17:22.730 --> 00:17:25.330
SHE'S A VERY ATTRACTIVE
WOMAN, BEATRICE.

00:17:25.330 --> 00:17:27.760
OR AT LEAST SHE WOULD
BE IF SHE WASN'T SUCH A

00:17:27.760 --> 00:17:30.060
SMALL, CARNIVOROUS
DINOSAUR.

00:17:30.060 --> 00:17:32.660
QUICK, SHARP, VICIOUS
LITTLE TEETH.

00:17:32.660 --> 00:17:34.300
VELOCIRAPTOR.

00:17:34.300 --> 00:17:38.060
EXACTLY,
VELOCIRAPTOR.

00:17:38.060 --> 00:17:40.830
WE WERE JUST TALKING ABOUT
A BIG NEW FOSSIL FIND, BEA.

00:17:40.830 --> 00:17:43.360
IT'S VERY EXCITING.

00:17:43.360 --> 00:17:45.200
DON'T CALL ME
BEA, PLEASE.

00:17:45.200 --> 00:17:47.230
THOUGHT YOU'D BE GENTLE
WITH ME TONIGHT.

00:17:47.230 --> 00:17:49.300
YOU'RE NOT SCARED,
ARE YOU?

00:17:49.300 --> 00:17:51.660
WELL, YOU DID NEARLY KILL
YOUR LAST CO-PRESENTER.

00:17:51.660 --> 00:17:53.060
THAT WAS JUSTIFIABLE
HOMICIDE.

00:17:53.060 --> 00:17:54.260
DID YOU MISS ME?

00:17:54.260 --> 00:17:55.930
YOU WERE ALL I
THOUGHT ABOUT.

00:17:55.930 --> 00:17:58.430
AM I TUGGING
IT TOO HARD?

00:17:58.430 --> 00:18:00.500
TUG HARDER IF
YOU WANT TO.

00:18:00.500 --> 00:18:02.060
OH, DEAR.

00:18:02.060 --> 00:18:03.660
NEED ANYTHING,
BEATRICE?

00:18:03.660 --> 00:18:06.030
A SHORT LENGTH
OF LEAD PIPE.

00:18:06.030 --> 00:18:08.300
ONE MINUTE THEN,
EVERYONE!

00:18:08.300 --> 00:18:11.960
CAN I SPEAK HONESTLY?

00:18:11.960 --> 00:18:14.060
I DON'T KNOW.
CAN YOU?

00:18:14.060 --> 00:18:16.530
BECAUSE CLEARLY YOU'RE
STILL UPSET ABOUT "US".

00:18:16.530 --> 00:18:17.830
US? OH, GOD.

00:18:17.830 --> 00:18:19.660
ABOUT THE WAY
IT ENDED.

00:18:19.660 --> 00:18:22.000
NOTHING HAD STARTED, BEN,
SO HOW COULD IT END?

00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:24.630
YOU KNOW, I FEEL BAD ABOUT
TELLING YOU BY TEXT.

00:18:24.630 --> 00:18:28.060
THIS WOULD BE FUNNY IF
IT WASN'T SO PATHETIC.

00:18:28.060 --> 00:18:32.600
AND I'M SORRY, REALLY I AM, BUT
WE CAN'T GO ON LIKE THIS, BEA.

00:18:32.600 --> 00:18:34.600
DON'T CALL ME BEA!

00:18:34.600 --> 00:18:36.130
EVERYTHING HAPPY
IN THERE?

00:18:36.130 --> 00:18:37.230
FINE.

00:18:37.230 --> 00:18:38.930
PERFECT.

00:18:38.930 --> 00:18:40.900
<i>GOOD LUCK, AND
WE'RE ON IN 30.</i>

00:18:40.900 --> 00:18:42.930
YOU'VE GOT SOMETHING
IN YOUR TEETH.

