SURE I DO.
SPINACH, RIGHT?

00:18:44.730 --> 00:18:46.760
NO, JUST A STRINGY
BIT RIGHT THERE.

00:18:46.760 --> 00:18:48.500
I'LL LIVE WITH
IT, THANK YOU.

00:18:48.500 --> 00:18:50.730
OKAY, YOUR DECISION.

00:18:50.730 --> 00:18:55.130
YOU KNOW, IT REALLY IS THE
OLDEST TRICK IN THE BOOK.

00:18:55.130 --> 00:18:58.600
