BUT IF YOU DON'T BELIEVE ME.

00:18:58.600 --> 00:19:00.860
EIGHT, SEVEN...

00:19:00.860 --> 00:19:02.130
WHY DON'T YOU ASK
THE GUYS THEN?

00:19:02.130 --> 00:19:03.430
OKAY, I WILL.

00:19:03.430 --> 00:19:04.830
GO ON, THEN.

00:19:04.830 --> 00:19:06.630
GUYS, HAVE I GOT
SOMETHING IN MY TEETH?

00:19:06.630 --> 00:19:08.530
CUE BENEDICK.

00:19:08.530 --> 00:19:11.300
AND I'M
BEATRICE EVANS.

00:19:11.300 --> 00:19:13.200
WELCOME TO
WESSEX TONIGHT.

