PRICE OF ONE!

00:19:48.930 --> 00:19:51.630
LET'S THROW THIS OLD
STUFF OUT NOW, DAD.

00:19:51.630 --> 00:19:53.600
I'LL HELP YOU
IF YOU WANT.

00:19:53.600 --> 00:19:55.260
I LIKE IT THE
WAY IT IS.

00:19:55.260 --> 00:19:59.130
BESIDES, YOU NEVER KNOW WHEN
YOU MIGHT NEED YOUR ROOM BACK.

