SEE, MISS MUFFET'S
COMPLETELY DIFFERENT.

00:21:43.130 --> 00:21:44.930
I'VE GOT A SPIDER.

00:21:44.930 --> 00:21:46.630
JUST SOME OLD LEOTARD
I FOUND TANGLED UP

00:21:46.630 --> 00:21:48.330
IN MY LINGERIE
DRAWER.

