WELL, I PREFER TO THINK OF
MYSELF AS A BROADCASTER.

00:22:59.130 --> 00:23:00.960
YOU'RE MORE
THAN THAT.

00:23:00.960 --> 00:23:03.000
YOU'RE A
COMMUNICATOR.

00:23:03.000 --> 00:23:04.760
THANK YOU, BEN.

00:23:04.760 --> 00:23:06.530
MARGARET'S
LOOKING FOR YOU.

