MINUTE, WOULD YOU?

00:24:31.800 --> 00:24:33.630
CLAUDE?

00:24:33.630 --> 00:24:36.930
WHAT? IS IT
SOMETHING I'VE SAID?

00:24:36.930 --> 00:24:39.530
CLAUDE?

00:24:46.100 --> 00:24:48.360
