IT'S OBVIOUS, REALLY.

01:10:04.260 --> 01:10:06.130
STOP THIS
PLEASE, CLAUDE.

01:10:06.130 --> 01:10:08.560
HERE'S A CLUE.

01:10:08.560 --> 01:10:11.030
HOW ABOUT LYING?

01:10:11.030 --> 01:10:15.200
HOW ABOUT THE FACT SHE'S A
LYING, CHEATING, SCHEMING,

01:10:15.200 --> 01:10:16.930
DECEITFUL BITCH!

01:10:16.930 --> 01:10:18.430
WHAT DID YOU SAY?

01:10:18.430 --> 01:10:20.360
YOU'RE HERE TO GIVE HER AWAY,
LEONARD, IS THAT RIGHT?

01:10:20.360 --> 01:10:23.030
WELL, I DON'T WANT HER.
SHE'S ROTTEN GOODS.

01:10:23.030 --> 01:10:26.230
HERE, YOU CAN
TAKE HER BACK.

01:10:26.230 --> 01:10:29.730
LOOK AT HER! THE BLUSHING
BRIDE, ALL INNOCENT.

01:10:29.730 --> 01:10:32.100
YOU'D NEVER GUESS
FROM THAT FACE

01:10:32.100 --> 01:10:34.600
WHAT A DISHONEST LITTLE
TART SHE REALLY IS.

01:10:34.600 --> 01:10:36.300
COME HERE YOU!

01:10:36.300 --> 01:10:38.100
I DON'T UNDERSTAND WHY
ARE YOU DOING THIS?

01:10:38.100 --> 01:10:39.930
I KNOW THE
TRUTH, HERO!

01:10:39.930 --> 01:10:41.860
I KNOW ABOUT
THE TWO OF YOU.

01:10:41.860 --> 01:10:44.660
THE SECRET MEETINGS,
THE PICNICS ON THE BEACH,

01:10:44.660 --> 01:10:47.100
THE MESSAGES,
THE PHOTOGRAPHS.

01:10:47.100 --> 01:10:48.960
WHAT MESSAGES?
WHAT PHOTOGRAPHS?

01:10:48.960 --> 01:10:51.460
I SAW HIM GO TO
YOUR ROOM, HERO.

01:10:51.460 --> 01:10:53.460
I SAW YOU KISS HIM.

01:10:53.460 --> 01:10:55.630
I SAW YOU PUT YOUR
ARMS AROUND HIM.

01:10:55.630 --> 01:10:57.900
I WAS WAITING
OUTSIDE.

01:10:57.900 --> 01:11:01.500
THE NIGHT BEFORE
YOUR WEDDING, HERO?

01:11:01.500 --> 01:11:04.560
WHO? DON? ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT DON?

01:11:04.560 --> 01:11:08.430
SORRY, HERO. I
HAD TO TELL HIM.

01:11:08.430 --> 01:11:09.930
THAT DON?

01:11:09.930 --> 01:11:13.500
WAS HE OR WASN'T HE IN
YOUR ROOM LAST NIGHT?

01:11:13.500 --> 01:11:18.630
NO! I MEAN, YES, HE CAME TO
MY ROOM BUT JUST TO TALK.

01:11:18.630 --> 01:11:20.560
I FELT SORRY FOR HIM.

01:11:20.560 --> 01:11:23.530
FELT SORRY FOR HIM?
THAT'S A GOOD ONE!

01:11:23.530 --> 01:11:26.260
AND HOW MAN OTHER MEN
HAVE YOU FELT SORRY FOR?

01:11:26.260 --> 01:11:28.760
STOP THIS, CLAUDE.
YOU'RE BEING RIDICULOUS.

01:11:28.760 --> 01:11:30.430
ALRIGHT, ONE MORE
QUESTION THEN.

01:11:30.430 --> 01:11:32.500
ANSWER ME THIS.

01:11:32.500 --> 01:11:34.930
HAVE YOU SLEPT
WITH HIM?

01:11:34.930 --> 01:11:38.960
DENY IT. GO ON.
HERE, IN CHURCH.

01:11:38.960 --> 01:11:46.160
PLEASE HERO. I WANT SO
MUCH FOR YOU TO DENY IT.

01:11:46.160 --> 01:11:51.060
ANSWER HIM,
SWEETHEART.

01:11:51.060 --> 01:11:56.960
I THOUGHT YOU
LOVED ME, CLAUDE.

01:11:56.960 --> 01:12:02.060
IF YOU LOVED ME YOU
WOULDN'T DO THIS TO ME.

01:12:02.060 --> 01:12:05.960
AND YOU'VE BROKEN
MY HEART, CLAUDE.

01:12:05.960 --> 01:12:12.760
SHE DIDN'T DENY IT, LEONARD.
SHE DIDN'T DENY IT.

01:12:37.860 --> 01:12:42.030
THEY'VE TAKEN HER
BACK TO THE HOTEL.

01:12:42.030 --> 01:12:45.830
TRY AND CALM
HER DOWN.

01:12:45.830 --> 01:12:48.960
I CAN'T BELIEVE I
WROTE A SPEECH.

01:12:48.960 --> 01:12:55.760
GENERALLY SPEAKING I
THINK IT WENT PRETTY WELL.

01:12:55.760 --> 01:12:58.530
YOU'RE CRYING.

01:12:58.530 --> 01:13:03.760
YES. AND I INTEND TO
CRY A LITTLE LONGER.

01:13:03.760 --> 01:13:05.960
I HATE
SEEING YOU CRY.

01:13:05.960 --> 01:13:08.700
WELL, DON'T WORRY.
IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT.

01:13:08.700 --> 01:13:11.460
NOT THIS
TIME ANYWAY.

01:13:19.430 --> 01:13:21.400
YOU KNOW, THERE'S
NOTHING IN THIS WORLD

01:13:21.400 --> 01:13:23.860
I LOVE AS
MUCH AS YOU.

01:13:23.860 --> 01:13:26.230
ISN'T THAT STRANGE?

01:13:26.230 --> 01:13:31.000
ALMOST AS STRANGE AS IF
I WERE TO SAY I LOVE YOU.

01:13:31.000 --> 01:13:34.700
I'D BEEN LED TO
BELIEVE - TO HOPE -

01:13:34.700 --> 01:13:41.460
THAT PERHAPS
THAT WAS THE CASE.

01:13:41.460 --> 01:13:44.960
I LOVE YOU, BEATRICE.

01:13:44.960 --> 01:13:47.030
THERE YOU GO.

01:13:47.030 --> 01:13:49.630
I'VE NEVER SAID
THAT BEFORE.

01:13:49.630 --> 01:13:52.560
WELL, IT MIGHT HAVE
SLIPPED OUT ONCE OR TWICE

01:13:52.560 --> 01:13:55.230
IN THE HEAT OF
THE MOMENT.

01:13:55.230 --> 01:13:58.630
BUT I NEVER THOUGHT
I'D SAY IT AND MEAN IT.

01:13:58.630 --> 01:14:00.360
BEN.

01:14:00.360 --> 01:14:03.000
I LOVE YOU SO MUCH, BEATRICE,
THAT IF I CAN'T HAVE YOU

01:14:03.000 --> 01:14:04.860
I THINK I'LL GO MAD.

01:14:04.860 --> 01:14:06.600
THEN I'M SORRY,
BENEDICK.

01:14:06.600 --> 01:14:08.560
WHAT ARE YOU SORRY
FOR, BEATRICE?

01:14:08.560 --> 01:14:11.830
YOU'VE CAUGHT ME AT
A VERY UNHAPPY TIME.

01:14:11.830 --> 01:14:15.160
I WAS ABOUT TO SAY
I LOVED YOU TOO.

01:14:15.160 --> 01:14:18.100
WELL, SAY IT THEN.

01:14:18.100 --> 01:14:24.500
I LOVE YOU SO MUCH I
CAN HARDLY BREATHE.

01:14:29.360 --> 01:14:37.200
BEATRICE, I'LL DO ANYTHING FOR
YOU - ANYTHING YOU ASK.

01:14:37.200 --> 01:14:40.830
KILL CLAUDE.

01:14:40.830 --> 01:14:44.460
EXCEPT FOR
THAT MAYBE?

01:14:44.460 --> 01:14:47.300
WHY NOT? I FEEL
LIKE KILLING HIM.

01:14:47.300 --> 01:14:49.260
I'M SURE HE HAD
HIS REASONS.

01:14:49.260 --> 01:14:53.260
WHAT REASONS COULD
HE POSSIBLY HAVE FOR

01:14:53.260 --> 01:14:56.360
HUMILIATING THE POOR GIRL
LIKE THAT ON HER WEDDING DAY?

01:14:56.360 --> 01:14:58.400
WHAT KIND OF VICIOUS...

01:14:58.400 --> 01:15:00.760
GET AWAY FROM ME!

01:15:00.760 --> 01:15:02.900
ON HER WEDDING DAY!

01:15:02.900 --> 01:15:04.900
AT THE ALTAR!

01:15:04.900 --> 01:15:07.600
TO DO THAT TO THE
WOMAN YOU CLAIM TO LOVE...

01:15:07.600 --> 01:15:10.300
I SWEAR IF I WAS A MAN
I WOULD EAT HIS HEART!

01:15:10.300 --> 01:15:14.360
BUT WHY WOULD I WANT TO BE
A MAN? YOU'RE ALL THE SAME.

01:15:14.360 --> 01:15:18.260
HERE HE STANDS SPEWING OUT THIS
FILTH, THIS POISON AT HERO WHO'S

01:15:18.260 --> 01:15:21.830
NEVER HURT ANYONE IN HER ENTIRE
LIFE, AND WHAT DO YOU ALL DO?

01:15:21.830 --> 01:15:26.200
YOU BRAVE, HONORABLE MEN,
YOU JUST STAND THERE...

01:15:26.200 --> 01:15:31.730
USELESS, LISTENING TO
THIS SLANDER, THESE LIES!

01:15:31.730 --> 01:15:36.260
DON'T YOU DARE WALK AWAY FROM
ME WHEN I'M SHOUTING AT YOU!

01:15:44.030 --> 01:15:46.930
I LOVE YOU, BEATRICE.

01:15:46.930 --> 01:15:52.000
AND I'M GOING TO MAKE
EVERYTHING ALL RIGHT.

01:16:05.630 --> 01:16:07.100
AH, THERE YOU ARE.

01:16:07.100 --> 01:16:09.500
I WONDER IF I
COULD HAVE A WORD.

01:16:09.500 --> 01:16:12.160
I SWEAR, MR. BARRY, IF
YOU ASK TO SEE MY ID...

01:16:12.160 --> 01:16:15.230
ACTUALLY, I THINK WE MIGHT HAVE
AN EXPLANATION FOR ALL THIS.

01:16:15.230 --> 01:16:17.560
IT'LL ONLY
TAKE A MINUTE.

01:16:20.830 --> 01:16:22.200
OH!

01:16:22.200 --> 01:16:25.730
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN, LET'S
HEAR IT FOR THE BEST MAN.

01:16:25.730 --> 01:16:27.200
CLAUDE,
YOU'RE DRUNK.

01:16:27.200 --> 01:16:29.100
I BLOODY HOPE SO.

01:16:29.100 --> 01:16:34.260
THE BOSS IS PAYING - OR
SHOULD I SAY, EX-BOSS.

01:16:34.260 --> 01:16:37.230
IF YOU'RE HUNGRY, 250
PORTIONS OF SALMON...

01:16:37.230 --> 01:16:40.260
I NEED TO TALK
WITH YOU. ALONE.

01:16:40.260 --> 01:16:43.660
FINE. I KNOW WHEN
I'M NOT WANTED.

01:16:43.660 --> 01:16:46.230
GOOD. YOU'RE NOT
WANTED, SO GO.

01:16:46.230 --> 01:16:49.960
NO, DON, YOU
STAY HERE. DON?

01:16:49.960 --> 01:16:52.430
WHOA, WHAT YOU
GONNA DO, HIT ME?

01:16:52.430 --> 01:16:55.060
I AM TRYING
HARD NOT TO.

01:16:55.060 --> 01:16:58.360
CLAUDE, YOU KNOW YOU'VE DONE
SOMETHING TERRIBLE, DON'T YOU?

01:16:58.360 --> 01:17:01.660
WELL, SEE, THAT, MY FRIEND,
IS A MATTER OF OPINION.

01:17:01.660 --> 01:17:05.130
YOU'RE NOT MY FRIEND AND
IT'S NOT A MATTER OF OPINION.

01:17:05.130 --> 01:17:08.530
HE'S TRICKED YOU, CLAUDE.
HE'S MADE YOU LOOK A FOOL.

01:17:08.530 --> 01:17:10.430
WHO, DON?

01:17:10.430 --> 01:17:12.830
I DON'T THINK SO.
I'VE SEEN THE PROOF.

01:17:12.830 --> 01:17:14.830
WHAT PROOF, CLAUDE?

01:17:14.830 --> 01:17:17.130
THE PHOTOS.

01:17:17.130 --> 01:17:19.360
HE STOLE THEM
FROM HERO'S ROOM.

01:17:19.360 --> 01:17:21.830
MR. BARRY HERE
SAW HIM.

01:17:21.830 --> 01:17:24.360
THAT'S RIGHT. THE
NIGHT OF THE PARTY.

01:17:24.360 --> 01:17:27.160
AND TEXT MESSAGES.

01:17:27.160 --> 01:17:28.900
HE USED HER PHONE.

01:17:28.900 --> 01:17:32.900
HE'S BEEN BORROWING HER PHONE
AND TEXTING HIS OWN NUMBER!

01:17:32.900 --> 01:17:35.860
WHAT ABOUT ON HER HEN NIGHT,
HOW DID HE GET HER PHONE THEN?

01:17:35.860 --> 01:17:37.830
HE HAD HER
BAG, REMEMBER?

01:17:37.830 --> 01:17:39.760
HE GAVE IT TO HER IN THE
CORRIDOR. I SAW HIM.

01:17:39.760 --> 01:17:41.930
YOU WERE THERE.

01:17:45.400 --> 01:17:48.060
NO, NO, THIS
IS RIDICULOUS.

01:17:48.060 --> 01:17:52.760
I SAW HIM GO TO HER ROOM
LAST NIGHT. I WAS THERE.

01:17:52.760 --> 01:17:54.330
IN HER ROOM?

01:17:54.330 --> 01:17:56.800
NO, OUTSIDE,
BUT... I SAW...

01:17:56.800 --> 01:17:59.860
YOU SAW WHAT YOU
WANTED TO SEE, CLAUDE.

01:17:59.860 --> 01:18:02.500
YOU SAW WHAT HE
TOLD YOU TO SEE.

01:18:09.130 --> 01:18:12.830
WHY WOULD HE
DO ALL THIS?

01:18:12.830 --> 01:18:15.860
JUST SO YOU KNOW, BEATRICE
IS BRINGING HER DOWN NOW.

01:18:15.860 --> 01:18:19.960
HERO, OH, I'VE GOT
TO TALK TO HER.

01:18:19.960 --> 01:18:21.400
NOT NOW, CLAUDE.

01:18:21.400 --> 01:18:23.230
I NEED TO
SPEAK TO HER.

01:18:23.230 --> 01:18:24.500
NOT NOW.

01:18:24.500 --> 01:18:26.360
NO, I NEED TO
SPEAK TO HER!

01:18:26.360 --> 01:18:27.860
LET GO OF ME!

01:18:27.860 --> 01:18:30.230
YOU.

01:18:30.230 --> 01:18:32.660
I WANT TO TALK
TO YOU, DON.

01:18:32.660 --> 01:18:34.830
HERO, I THINK I
MIGHT HAVE MADE A...

01:18:34.830 --> 01:18:36.060
NOT NOW, CLAUDE.

01:18:36.060 --> 01:18:37.700
I NEED TO SAY...

01:18:37.700 --> 01:18:39.960
I THINK YOU'VE SAID QUITE
ENOUGH ALREADY, DON'T YOU?

01:18:39.960 --> 01:18:41.360
HE SHOWED ME PHOTOS...

01:18:41.360 --> 01:18:43.460
I SAID SHUT UP!

01:18:43.460 --> 01:18:49.300
IT'S HIM I WANT
TO TALK TO.

01:18:49.300 --> 01:18:53.160
ONE QUESTION.

01:18:53.160 --> 01:18:59.700
TELL ME WHY, DON, BECAUSE
I NEED TO UNDERSTAND.

01:18:59.700 --> 01:19:06.260
WASN'T I KIND TO YOU?
AFFECTIONATE? A GOOD FRIEND?

01:19:06.260 --> 01:19:10.230
DIDN'T I LISTEN TO YOU TALK
ON AND ON INTO THE NIGHT?

01:19:10.230 --> 01:19:14.800
AND DIDN'T I TELL YOU THE
WAY I FELT ABOUT YOU?

01:19:14.800 --> 01:19:18.100
WASN'T I HONEST?

01:19:18.100 --> 01:19:25.200
SO TELL ME, WHY WOULD
YOU DO THIS TO ME, DON?

01:19:25.200 --> 01:19:28.260
BECAUSE I LOVE YOU.

01:19:28.260 --> 01:19:32.500
AND YOU
HUMILIATED ME.

01:19:32.500 --> 01:19:38.760
AND I WANTED YOU TO KNOW
WHAT THAT FELT LIKE.

01:19:38.760 --> 01:19:40.830
HERO, NO!

01:19:40.830 --> 01:19:44.930
I HATE YOU! I HATE YOU!

01:19:44.930 --> 01:19:47.530
SWEETHEART!

01:19:47.530 --> 01:19:51.460
ARE YOU ALRIGHT?

01:19:51.460 --> 01:19:53.660
OH!

01:19:53.660 --> 01:19:56.000
GIVE HER SOME AIR.

01:19:56.000 --> 01:19:59.160
I'M SORRY, I'M SORRY,
I'M SO SORRY!

01:19:59.160 --> 01:20:02.900
CALL AN AMBULANCE.

01:20:34.930 --> 01:20:36.530
HEY.

01:20:36.530 --> 01:20:38.000
I GOT YOU THIS.

01:20:38.000 --> 01:20:39.230
WHAT IS IT?

01:20:39.230 --> 01:20:40.700
COFFEE.

01:20:40.700 --> 01:20:42.330
MAYBE SOUP.

01:20:42.330 --> 01:20:46.200
THANKS, I
THINK I'LL PASS.

01:20:46.200 --> 01:20:48.660
POOR OLD LEONARD.

01:20:48.660 --> 01:20:50.430
WHAT DO WE DO NOW?

01:20:50.430 --> 01:20:54.000
WAIT AND SEE WHAT
THE TESTS SAY.

01:20:54.000 --> 01:20:56.360
IT'S NOT GOOD, I'M AFRAID.

01:20:56.360 --> 01:20:59.900
SHE'S STILL NOT CONSCIOUS.

01:20:59.900 --> 01:21:02.360
THEY'LL DO MORE TESTS
IN THE MORNING.

01:21:02.360 --> 01:21:04.560
AND MAYBE OPERATE.

01:21:04.560 --> 01:21:08.460
ALL WE CAN DO NOW IS
GO HOME AND SLEEP.

01:21:08.460 --> 01:21:13.500
THANKS PETE.

01:21:13.500 --> 01:21:17.200
LET ME TAKE
YOU HOME.

01:21:17.200 --> 01:21:19.500
I'M SORRY, BEN.

01:21:19.500 --> 01:21:21.460
WHAT FOR?

01:21:21.460 --> 01:21:24.630
WE HAVE SOMETHING TO
TALK ABOUT, DON'T WE?

01:21:24.630 --> 01:21:29.200
AND NOW DOESN'T REALLY
SEEM LIKE THE RIGHT TIME.

01:21:29.200 --> 01:21:32.260
IT CAN WAIT.

01:22:04.800 --> 01:22:08.330
SO, HERE WE ARE.

01:22:16.360 --> 01:22:18.130
I'M SORRY.

01:22:18.130 --> 01:22:25.060
I THOUGHT WHEN I SAW YOU IT
WOULD ALL COME FLOODING OUT,

01:22:25.060 --> 01:22:29.730
YOU KNOW? SOME SPECIAL
COMBINATION OF WORDS

01:22:29.730 --> 01:22:35.830
TO TELL YOU HOW
SORRY I AM.

01:22:35.830 --> 01:22:39.160
AND HOW MUCH
I LOVE YOU.

01:22:39.160 --> 01:22:42.900
AND MISS YOU.

01:22:42.900 --> 01:22:44.960
BUT THEY'RE NOT MY
STRONG POINT, ARE THEY?

01:22:44.960 --> 01:22:46.660
WORDS.

01:22:46.660 --> 01:22:49.800
THEY WON'T DO WHAT
I WANT THEM TO.

01:22:49.800 --> 01:22:58.460
SO I'LL JUST HAVE TO SAY THAT
I WOULD HAPPILY GIVE MY LIFE

01:22:58.460 --> 01:23:03.530
RIGHT NOW IF YOU'LL JUST OPEN
YOUR EYES AND SAY SOMETHING.

01:23:03.530 --> 01:23:07.400
ANYTHING - EVEN IF IT'S TO
SAY THAT YOU HATE ME.

01:23:07.400 --> 01:23:11.330
BECAUSE IF YOU DON'T,
HERO, I REALLY DON'T KNOW

01:23:11.330 --> 01:23:13.900
WHAT I'M GONNA DO.

01:23:13.900 --> 01:23:17.530
SORRY, BUT I'M GOING TO
HAVE TO ASK YOU TO LEAVE.

01:23:17.530 --> 01:23:20.660
IMMEDIATELY, PLEASE.

01:23:30.160 --> 01:23:32.500
I'M SORRY.

01:23:49.900 --> 01:23:57.600
(BEEPING SOUND)

01:23:57.600 --> 01:24:00.560
WHAT'S HAPPENING?

01:24:00.560 --> 01:24:03.130
WHAT'S GOING ON?

01:24:03.130 --> 01:24:05.700
NO! HERO!

01:24:05.700 --> 01:24:07.560
YOU CAN'T
COME IN HERE.

01:24:07.560 --> 01:24:11.030
I NEED TO SEE HER!

01:24:11.030 --> 01:24:16.660
CLAUDE! WHO ARE
ALL THESE PEOPLE?

01:24:29.930 --> 01:24:32.260
EXCUSE ME, IS THERE
ANYONE SITTING HERE?

01:24:32.260 --> 01:24:35.160
WELL, ACTUALLY, I'M
WAITING FOR A FRIEND.

01:24:35.160 --> 01:24:38.830
WILL HE MIND IF I SIT
DOWN WHILE YOU WAIT?

01:24:46.930 --> 01:24:49.330
SO, AM I LATE?

01:24:49.330 --> 01:24:52.330
ONLY ABOUT
THREE YEARS.

01:24:59.630 --> 01:25:02.630
I'VE BEEN OFFERED
A JOB IN LONDON.

01:25:02.630 --> 01:25:05.300
IT'S JUST A PRODUCTION
JOB TO BEGIN WITH.

01:25:05.300 --> 01:25:07.460
MAYBE GET ON
SCREEN SOON.

01:25:07.460 --> 01:25:09.960
ARE YOU GOING
TO TAKE IT?

01:25:09.960 --> 01:25:13.060
I DON'T KNOW.

01:25:13.060 --> 01:25:18.030
IT'S A BIG STEP,
MOVING AWAY.

01:25:18.030 --> 01:25:23.060
I THINK YOU
SHOULD GO.

01:25:23.060 --> 01:25:26.200
CLAUDE, IF YOU'RE
EXPECTING ME TO FORGIVE YOU

01:25:26.200 --> 01:25:28.960
YOU'RE WASTING
YOUR TIME.

01:25:28.960 --> 01:25:31.930
BUT I ONLY DID IT
BECAUSE I LOVED YOU.

01:25:31.930 --> 01:25:35.430
FUNNY, THAT'S
WHAT DON SAID.

01:25:35.430 --> 01:25:40.430
I'M SO BORED OF PEOPLE
USING LOVE AS AN EXCUSE.

01:25:40.430 --> 01:25:47.200
THAT'S NOT LOVE ANYWAY,
THAT'S JUST POSSESSION,

01:25:47.200 --> 01:25:52.360
AND I'M BORED OF BEING
OWNED TOO, BY YOU, BY MY DAD.

01:25:52.360 --> 01:25:57.430
I'M JUST GOING TO LOOK
AFTER MYSELF FOR A WHILE.

01:25:57.430 --> 01:26:02.200
THINK THINGS THROUGH.

01:26:02.200 --> 01:26:10.260
WHEN YOU'VE HAD SOME TIME,
MAYBE YOU WOULD THINK ABOUT

01:26:10.260 --> 01:26:13.560
CARRYING ON
WHERE WE LEFT OFF?

01:26:13.560 --> 01:26:16.560
WHAT, GET MARRIED?
TO YOU?

01:26:16.560 --> 01:26:19.830
NEVER IN A
MILLION YEARS.

01:26:19.830 --> 01:26:22.730
OKAY, MAYBE NOT IN
THE SHORT TERM, BUT...

01:26:22.730 --> 01:26:27.730
SOME TIME IN THE
FUTURE PERHAPS?

01:26:27.730 --> 01:26:33.360
JUST SAY I CAN HOPE,
HERO, PLEASE?

01:26:33.360 --> 01:26:36.800
PLEASE?

01:26:51.060 --> 01:26:59.230
"LET ME NOT TO THE MARRIAGE
OF TRUE MINDS ADMIT TO, UH.

01:26:59.230 --> 01:27:05.660
LET ME NOT TO THE MARRIAGE OF
TRUE MINDS ADMIT IMPEDIMENTS.

01:27:05.660 --> 01:27:08.230
HEY, COME ON!
EVERYONE'S WAITING.

01:27:08.230 --> 01:27:10.460
HERE, YOU LOOK GOOD.

01:27:10.460 --> 01:27:12.160
ALL RIGHT?

01:27:12.160 --> 01:27:13.730
YEAH.

01:27:13.730 --> 01:27:15.900
